title: I need help guys :(
body:
So I used to be Gold V but I massively dropped recently, because my duo-partner stopped playing...I'm now at silver III. I main support :3. Is anyone out there willing to help a damsel in distress? 
Or maybe some people for normals :)

-not looking for a boost but for someone that's fun to play with!

replies.body: German guys here with curry wurst and beer!!!
